            'Romani 6:6; Romani 6:7; Romani 8:2; Romani 8:3': '<h3> <span>Romani 6:6</span></h3><p> <span><sup>6&#xA0;</sup>&#x15E;tim bine c&#x103; omul<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28075A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28075A"></sup> nostru cel vechi a fost r&#x103;stignit &#xEE;mpreun&#x103; cu El, pentru ca trupul<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28075B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28075B"></sup> p&#x103;catului s&#x103; fie dezbr&#x103;cat de puterea lui, &#xEE;n a&#x15F;a fel ca s&#x103; nu mai fim robi ai p&#x103;catului,</span> </p><h3> <span>Romani 6:7</span></h3><p> <span><sup>7&#xA0;</sup>c&#x103;ci cine<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28076A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28076A"></sup> a murit, de drept, este izb&#x103;vit de p&#x103;cat.</span> </p><h3> <span>Romani 8:2</span></h3><p> <span><sup>2&#xA0;</sup>&#xCE;n adev&#x103;r, legea<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28119A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28119A"></sup> Duhului<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28119B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28119B"></sup> de via&#x163;&#x103; &#xEE;n Hristos Isus m-a izb&#x103;vit de legea<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28119C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28119C"></sup> p&#x103;catului &#x15F;i a mor&#x163;ii.</span> </p><h3> <span>Romani 8:3</span></h3><p> <span><sup>3&#xA0;</sup>C&#x103;ci &#x2013; lucru<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28120A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28120A"></sup> cu neputin&#x163;&#x103; Legii, &#xEE;ntruc&#xE2;t firea p&#x103;m&#xE2;nteasc&#x103; o f&#x103;cea f&#x103;r&#x103; putere &#x2013; Dumnezeu<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28120B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28120B"></sup> a os&#xE2;ndit p&#x103;catul &#xEE;n firea p&#x103;m&#xE2;nteasc&#x103;, trimi&#x163;&#xE2;nd, din pricina p&#x103;catului, pe &#xCE;nsu&#x15F;i Fiul S&#x103;u &#xEE;ntr-o fire asem&#x103;n&#x103;toare cu a p&#x103;catului,</span> </p>'
            'Galateni 3:23-25; 4:7-8': '<h3> <span>Galateni 3:23-25</span></h3><p> <span><sup>23&#xA0;</sup>&#xCE;nainte de venirea credin&#x163;ei, noi eram sub paza Legii, &#xEE;nchi&#x15F;i pentru credin&#x163;a care trebuia s&#x103; fie descoperit&#x103;.</span> <span><sup>24&#xA0;</sup>Astfel, Legea<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29127A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29127A"></sup> ne-a fost un &#xEE;ndrum&#x103;tor spre Hristos, ca<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29127B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29127B"></sup> s&#x103; fim socoti&#x163;i neprih&#x103;ni&#x163;i prin credin&#x163;&#x103;.</span> <span><sup>25&#xA0;</sup>Dup&#x103; ce a venit credin&#x163;a, nu mai suntem sub &#xEE;ndrum&#x103;torul acesta.</span> </p><h3> <span>Galateni 4:7-8</span></h3><p> <span><sup>7&#xA0;</sup>A&#x15F;a c&#x103; nu mai e&#x15F;ti rob, ci fiu; &#x15F;i dac&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29139A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29139A"></sup> e&#x15F;ti fiu, e&#x15F;ti &#x15F;i mo&#x15F;tenitor prin Dumnezeu.</span></p><p><span><sup>8&#xA0;</sup>Odinioar&#x103;, c&#xE2;nd nu cuno&#x15F;tea&#x163;i<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29140B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29140B"></sup> pe Dumnezeu, era&#x163;i robi&#x163;i<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29140C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29140C"></sup> celor ce, din firea lor, nu sunt dumnezei.</span> </p>'
            '1 Corinteni 15:55': '<h3> <span>1 Corinteni 15:55</span></h3><p> <span><sup>55&#xA0;</sup>Unde &#xEE;&#x163;i este biruin&#x163;a, moarte<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28774A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28774A"></sup>? Unde &#xEE;&#x163;i este boldul, moarte?&#x201D;</span> </p>'
            'Evrei 2:14,15': '<h3> <span>Evrei 2:14</span></h3><p> <span><sup>14&#xA0;</sup>Astfel dar, deoarece copiii sunt p&#x103;rta&#x15F;i s&#xE2;ngelui &#x15F;i c&#x103;rnii, tot a&#x15F;a &#x15F;i<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29992A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29992A"></sup> El &#xCE;nsu&#x15F;i a fost deopotriv&#x103; p&#x103;rta&#x15F; la ele, pentru ca<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29992B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29992B"></sup>, prin moarte, s&#x103; nimiceasc&#x103; pe cel ce are puterea mor&#x163;ii, adic&#x103; pe Diavolul,</span> </p><h3> <span>Evrei 2:15</span></h3><p> <span><sup>15&#xA0;</sup>&#x15F;i s&#x103; izb&#x103;veasc&#x103; pe to&#x163;i aceia care, prin frica mor&#x163;ii<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29993A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29993A"></sup>, erau supu&#x15F;i robiei toat&#x103; via&#x163;a lor.</span> </p>'
            'Galateni 2:4': '<h3> <span>Galateni 2:4</span></h3><p> <span><sup>4&#xA0;</sup>din pricina fra&#x163;ilor<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29086A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29086A"></sup> mincino&#x15F;i, furi&#x15F;a&#x163;i &#x15F;i strecura&#x163;i printre noi ca s&#x103; p&#xE2;ndeasc&#x103; slobozenia<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29086B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29086B"></sup> pe care o avem &#xEE;n Hristos Isus, cu g&#xE2;nd s&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29086C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29086C"></sup> ne aduc&#x103; la robie;</span> </p>'
            'Ioan 8:31-36': '<h3> <span>Ioan 8:31-36</span></h3><p> <span><sup>31&#xA0;</sup>&#x15E;i a zis iudeilor care crezuser&#x103; &#xEE;n El: <span>&#x201E;Dac&#x103; r&#x103;m&#xE2;ne&#x163;i &#xEE;n cuv&#xE2;ntul Meu, sunte&#x163;i &#xEE;n adev&#x103;r ucenicii Mei;</span></span> <span><sup>32&#xA0;</sup><span>ve&#x163;i cunoa&#x15F;te adev&#x103;rul</span><sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-26414A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-26414A"></sup><span>, &#x15F;i adev&#x103;rul v&#x103; va face slobozi&#x201D;</span>.</span> <span><sup>33&#xA0;</sup>Ei I-au r&#x103;spuns: &#x201E;Noi<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-26415B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-26415B"></sup> suntem s&#x103;m&#xE2;n&#x163;a lui Avraam &#x15F;i n-am fost niciodat&#x103; robii nim&#x103;nui. Cum zici Tu: <span>&#x2018;Ve&#x163;i fi slobozi&#x2019;</span>?&#x201D;</span> <span><sup>34&#xA0;</sup><span>&#x201E;Adev&#x103;rat, adev&#x103;rat v&#x103; spun&#x201D;</span>, le-a r&#x103;spuns Isus, <span>&#x201E;c&#x103; oricine</span><sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-26416C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-26416C"></sup> <span>tr&#x103;ie&#x15F;te &#xEE;n p&#x103;cat este rob al p&#x103;catului.</span></span> <span><sup>35&#xA0;</sup><span>&#x15E;i robul</span><sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-26417D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-26417D"></sup> <span>nu r&#x103;m&#xE2;ne pururea &#xEE;n cas&#x103;; fiul &#xEE;ns&#x103; r&#x103;m&#xE2;ne pururea.</span></span> <span><sup>36&#xA0;</sup><span>Deci, dac&#x103;</span><sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-26418E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-26418E"></sup> <span>Fiul v&#x103; face slobozi, ve&#x163;i fi cu adev&#x103;rat slobozi.</span></span> </p>'
            'Romani 8:1,2': '<h3> <span>Romani 8:1</span></h3><p><span><span>8&#xA0;</span>Acum dar nu este nicio os&#xE2;ndire pentru cei ce sunt &#xEE;n Hristos Isus, care nu<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28118A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28118A"></sup> tr&#x103;iesc dup&#x103; &#xEE;ndemnurile firii p&#x103;m&#xE2;nte&#x15F;ti, ci dup&#x103; &#xEE;ndemnurile Duhului.</span> </p><h3> <span>Romani 8:2</span></h3><p> <span><sup>2&#xA0;</sup>&#xCE;n adev&#x103;r, legea<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28119A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28119A"></sup> Duhului<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28119B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28119B"></sup> de via&#x163;&#x103; &#xEE;n Hristos Isus m-a izb&#x103;vit de legea<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28119C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28119C"></sup> p&#x103;catului &#x15F;i a mor&#x163;ii.</span> </p>'
            'Galateni 2:7': '<h3> <span>Galateni 2:7</span></h3><p> <span><sup>7&#xA0;</sup>Ba dimpotriv&#x103;, c&#xE2;nd au v&#x103;zut<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29089A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29089A"></sup> c&#x103; mie &#xEE;mi<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-29089B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-29089B"></sup> fusese &#xEE;ncredin&#x163;at&#x103; Evanghelia pentru cei net&#x103;ia&#x163;i &#xEE;mprejur, dup&#x103; cum lui Petru &#xEE;i fusese &#xEE;ncredin&#x163;at&#x103; Evanghelia pentru cei t&#x103;ia&#x163;i &#xEE;mprejur &#x2013;</span> </p>'
            'Romani 6': '<h3> <span>Romani 6</span></h3><p><span><span>6&#xA0;</span>Ce vom zice dar? S&#x103; p&#x103;c&#x103;tuim<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28070A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28070A"></sup> mereu ca s&#x103; se &#xEE;nmul&#x163;easc&#x103; harul?</span> <span><sup>2&#xA0;</sup>Nicidecum! Noi, care am<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28071B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28071B"></sup> murit fa&#x163;&#x103; de p&#x103;cat, cum s&#x103; mai tr&#x103;im &#xEE;n p&#x103;cat?</span> <span><sup>3&#xA0;</sup>Nu &#x15F;ti&#x163;i c&#x103; to&#x163;i c&#xE2;&#x163;i<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28072C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28072C"></sup> am fost boteza&#x163;i &#xEE;n Isus Hristos, am fost boteza&#x163;i &#xEE;n<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28072D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28072D"></sup> moartea Lui?</span> <span><sup>4&#xA0;</sup>Noi, deci, prin botezul &#xEE;n moartea Lui, am fost &#xEE;ngropa&#x163;i<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28073E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28073E"></sup> &#xEE;mpreun&#x103; cu El, pentru ca, dup&#x103; cum<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28073F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28073F"></sup> Hristos a &#xEE;nviat din mor&#x163;i prin slava<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28073G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28073G"></sup> Tat&#x103;lui, tot a&#x15F;a<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28073H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28073H"></sup> &#x15F;i noi s&#x103; tr&#x103;im o via&#x163;&#x103; nou&#x103;.</span> <span><sup>5&#xA0;</sup>&#xCE;n adev&#x103;r, dac&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28074I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28074I"></sup> ne-am f&#x103;cut una cu El printr-o moarte asem&#x103;n&#x103;toare cu a Lui, vom fi una cu El &#x15F;i printr-o &#xEE;nviere asem&#x103;n&#x103;toare cu a Lui.</span> <span><sup>6&#xA0;</sup>&#x15E;tim bine c&#x103; omul<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28075J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28075J"></sup> nostru cel vechi a fost r&#x103;stignit &#xEE;mpreun&#x103; cu El, pentru ca trupul<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28075K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28075K"></sup> p&#x103;catului s&#x103; fie dezbr&#x103;cat de puterea lui, &#xEE;n a&#x15F;a fel ca s&#x103; nu mai fim robi ai p&#x103;catului,</span> <span><sup>7&#xA0;</sup>c&#x103;ci cine<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28076L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28076L"></sup> a murit, de drept, este izb&#x103;vit de p&#x103;cat.</span> <span><sup>8&#xA0;</sup>Acum, dac&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28077M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28077M"></sup> am murit &#xEE;mpreun&#x103; cu Hristos, credem c&#x103; vom &#x15F;i tr&#x103;i &#xEE;mpreun&#x103; cu El,</span> <span><sup>9&#xA0;</sup>&#xEE;ntruc&#xE2;t &#x15F;tim c&#x103; Hristosul<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28078N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28078N"></sup> &#xEE;nviat din mor&#x163;i nu mai moare; moartea nu mai are nicio st&#x103;p&#xE2;nire asupra Lui.</span> <span><sup>10&#xA0;</sup>Fiindc&#x103; prin moartea de care a murit, El a<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28079O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28079O"></sup> murit pentru p&#x103;cat o dat&#x103; pentru totdeauna, iar prin via&#x163;a pe care o tr&#x103;ie&#x15F;te, tr&#x103;ie&#x15F;te<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28079P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28079P"></sup> pentru Dumnezeu.</span> <span><sup>11&#xA0;</sup>Tot a&#x15F;a &#x15F;i voi &#xEE;n&#x15F;iv&#x103; socoti&#x163;i-v&#x103; mor&#x163;i<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28080Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28080Q"></sup> fa&#x163;&#x103; de p&#x103;cat &#x15F;i vii<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28080R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28080R"></sup> pentru Dumnezeu, &#xEE;n Isus Hristos, Domnul nostru.</span> <span><sup>12&#xA0;</sup>Deci<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28081S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28081S"></sup> p&#x103;catul s&#x103; nu mai domneasc&#x103; &#xEE;n trupul vostru muritor &#x15F;i s&#x103; nu mai asculta&#x163;i de poftele lui.</span> <span><sup>13&#xA0;</sup>S&#x103; nu mai da&#x163;i &#xEE;n st&#x103;p&#xE2;nirea p&#x103;catului m&#x103;dularele<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28082T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28082T"></sup> voastre, ca ni&#x15F;te unelte ale nelegiuirii, ci da&#x163;i-v&#x103;<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28082U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)" data-cr="#cro-RMNN-28082U"></sup> pe voi &#xEE;n&#x15F;iv&#x103; lui Dumnezeu, ca vii, din mor&#x163;i cum era&#x163;i &#x15F;i da&#x163;i lui Dumnezeu m&#x103;dularele voastre, ca pe ni&#x15F;te unelte ale neprih&#x103;nirii.</span> <span><sup>14&#xA0;</sup>C&#x103;ci<sup data-link="(&lt;a href=&quot;#cro-RMNN-28083V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)" data